# CODEOWNERS
# Each line is a file pattern followed by one or more owners.
# Owners are automatically requested for review when someone opens a PR
# that modifies the matched files.
#
# Syntax: <pattern> <owner> [<owner>...]
# Examples:
#   *                   @org/team         # all files → whole team
#   /docs/              @org/docs-team    # docs folder
#   *.yml               @org/devops       # all YAML files

# Default owner for everything
# * @your-org/maintainers

# CI/CD and GitHub config
# .github/ @your-org/devops

# Documentation
# /docs/ @your-org/docs-team
